Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:46.07,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:16.45,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:45.79,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:55.80,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:02.72,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:17.42,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:16.48,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.{hasn't actually streamed yet. This is speculation}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With your new bond, you have awakened to the Star Arcana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, your story is drawing toward its climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, I imagine several surprises are laying in wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fate is at a crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail to solve the mystery, your future may close before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how thick the fog may appear, there is but one truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat isn't the only thing that can bring your story to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You would do well to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's definitely him. He's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise, you have a better nose than I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still wearing that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel more at home when I wear it on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so beary dense?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "Catch me if you can," so he probably thinks of this as a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I sentence him to a kick in the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That creep from the Midnight Channel is in here, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare he mumble a challenge with those beady fish eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The prick pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for the ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All dudes like games!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the ladies like Teddie. Bear-sona!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Booyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I look awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, oh my! Coming from bear-hind's a cowardly thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Teddie be okay on his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Chie and I were talking and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, no, no, no!{overlaps}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We think that guy who showed up on Midnight Channel might be the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We were thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadduya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The suspect is a high school boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Take this!{overlaps}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,After he killed King Moron, the police caught on to his trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And this!{overlaps}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And this!{overlaps}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention the Midnight Channel last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To top it off, his "catch me if you can" sounded awfully suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy came by my shop once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was selling tofu when he came up to me and started talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he was ranting about how biker gangs can't do anything unless they're in a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not in a gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He came up to Yukiko once, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He was by our school gate and called out, "Yukiko!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's all coming together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So he escaped to the TV world when he realized the cops were after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's still so much we don't know, like why he targeted people who were shown on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to ask him personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We're finally gonna get our guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:04:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We just gotta catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's as good as ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we done getting together like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Everyone's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they leave us bear-hind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pretty heartless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, my! Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am nothing, and you are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the killer's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It was me! I did it!{overlapping}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Look, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No one even suspected it was me.{background}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I did the third one in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him, you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what an imposter like you has to say!{impostor?}{either}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't accept me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Damn, this just {\i1}had{\i0} to happen!{overlapping}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall put an end to your emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, listen, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go to Yuki's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Parties! Traditional rooms! Hot springs! Yukata!{in the dictionary, i swear} Geisha! Mt. Fuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That sounds like fun, but today isn't the best day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tourist season since it's summer and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we go to Narukami's place instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanna go see his house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can let Nanako in on the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure she'd be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't we make her a feast?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you guys good at cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure... I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you seriously forget about the whole school camping fiasco?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm good at cooking, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to cook for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you can best me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought of a bear-y wonderful idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We could have a cook off with rice omelets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that foie gras{duck liver}?!{he stutters different syllables}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an absolute must if you want a special rice omelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly {\i1}seems{\i0} special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So the contest is between you and the three girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and Nanako will be the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm bound to win, the contest is just for show, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ku-Kujikawa, enjoy boasting while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish you in one blow.{you can finish me in one blow, yukiko}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, looks like the sparks are already flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Come to think of it, where's Teddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, you're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to try some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to cook some of that meat for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I'd get in trouble! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's he doing?{overlaps}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Amagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:08:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Yukiko's family suddenly called asking for help, so she had to rush back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We should save the celebration party for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that'd be for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So our cook off is canceled, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I wanted to bond with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So where'd these rice omelets come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu made all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we start eating, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, eat up before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll just help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, bear-y good indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about average.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's average.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're talented! Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You cool with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, it's just average, so the party's not picking up like it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I put wasabi in one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ru-Russian roulette with rice omelets?!{AMAZING}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude! What would you do if you served it to Nanako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your hand if you got a spicy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Maybe they didn't notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, this party's missing its zing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have had to postpone our celebration party, but man, the case is actually closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we caught the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been through a lot, but now we can get back to our normal lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to forget all that icky stuff quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I should go back to my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all going our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's meet up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we just gotta meet up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened with the case after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard anything since Kubo was caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd think everyone forgot about the case with the way no one mentions it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. The celebration party keeps getting postponed because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else has been busy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my hands full with my job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Her inn must be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great that everything's back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We never did get to go anywhere during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the beach together next year. Sound good, Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, you won't be here next year, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, about our summer homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, is this legit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rumors that she'd moved were true...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Rise say anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She hadn't been coming to our group meetings lately, so I thought something might've been up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The number you have dialed is currently not in service.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Women sure are scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she took off without telling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she had her reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it just goes to show we were the only ones who thought we were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We keep meeting over those murders, but there's nothing to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I think talking and trying to be all nice is exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a couple that's grown bored with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron, I was seriously asking for advice here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Studying for exams, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami, aren't you gonna borrow Amagi's notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry on over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No one comes over anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be nice if they dropped by to play sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's coming over?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, man, but I have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think Teddie's up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to go back inside the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with that crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, we should seriously start thinking about college and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do about entrance exams and stuff?{aree?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you start thinking about that now for when you go back to your old school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to get back to work. Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is "nothing."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You are alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You are empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My Arcana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it... You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1350)}I can't go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu! Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?{gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hit the Shadow until you destroy its outer shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet! There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's rebuilding his defenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dammit!{overlaps with previous line}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not on my watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Now's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit him nice and hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you take the spotlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,am not empty!{HOLY SHIT SQUEEEEE XD}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Makami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,King Frost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,High Pixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pyro Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight-Forked Serpent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How many Personas does he have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Leanan Sidhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rakshasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ara Mitama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are after you for killing King Moron on top of the other two murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one behind all these murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed them all! It was {\i1}me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? His Shadow vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:18:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone... the bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over now.{good series. would watch again.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,About Kubo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he confessed to everything, so all the cases are officially closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When asked why he did it, he said he wanted the attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like having a good reason would make it better, but you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave the rest to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's all we can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Our job here is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My world will be peaceful once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've sure been through a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Like stud hunting. Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you ever let that go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My Shadow did that, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was it like for you, Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Master really is one of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I guess we're done with our Personas, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this will be our last time meeting up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's meet up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer break, so of course we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already pals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, let's hold an afterparty.{yes, let us wrap presents. that's always fun}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good! We can celebrate solving the cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go all-out and party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the one Yukiko made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives? It has no taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I bit into raw wheat gluten.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's just too refined for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your rice omelet is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This tastes awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This definitely tastes awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were gonna defend me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's give Rise's a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know mine has hers beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Down in one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a taste too sophisticated for kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you're a bunch of kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spicy, but it's still good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, yours was definitely the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Big Bro's?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had a rice omelet like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:22:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all good, but I like Big Bro's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Glad to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time I headed back to my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going away somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since they kept their promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stay if you made a promise with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A promise with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Promise you'll come play with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinky promise! If I lie, stick a thousand needles in my eye.{da fuk. pick japanese or english. that's a weird combination of the two}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.14,0:23:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pinky promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how the shopping district is holding a festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.75,0:23:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadya say we all go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, that sounds good, Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.76,0:24:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You just called my big brother Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.31,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your business!{they're gay for each other}{otp}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.73,0:24:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me some space!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.94,0:24:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're pals!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.50,0:24:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}Don't use words you just learned!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of New Feather Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trailing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.09,0:24:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie got on a bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.04,0:24:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.75,0:24:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.67,0:24:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.86,0:24:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the mysterious detective, Loveline!
